rmal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有 不過唔係間間有<br />\ndetail自己上佢個官網store list有講邊d係tax free"},{"pid":"8add3c4d7f83492ff7148f5f836275bc4a076cf6","tid":150384,"uid":58207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T17:09:21.000Z","msg":"幾耐有得拎就要睇你去邊間金子眼鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為間間唔同 試過去台場就即試拎得 天神果間要等幾日<br />\n通常要我等都唔會等 我就會拎去街邊眼鏡舖<br />\n<br />\njins alook同zoff冇特別要求都即有 問過coolens都係要等幾日<br />\nalook就有兩個價3xxx同6000(己退稅) 其它果兩間好似5400(己退稅)<br />\njins會用hoya zoff唔知(佢無比番個袋我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) alook就nikon(6000果隻係 3XXX就唔知)<br />\n<br />\n基本上我配番戴開個度數 冇特別要求 3個字度就有得拎"},{"pid":"f74353b0fb6eee5a021ea07e8d174a4ba6a0a5ee","tid":150384,"uid":90266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T18:06:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H2f20Xs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH2f20Xs.jpg&h=74b4c96b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n半年前金子買 600度近視 200度散光 兩日就有得拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n剩架幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想配副yves"},{"pid":"5003202036aba1d9b93b1521905a6c2824ca2b20","tid":150384,"uid":90266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T18:07:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H2f20Xs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH2f20Xs.jpg&h=74b4c96b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n半年前金子買 600度近視 200度散光 兩日就有得拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n剩架幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想配副yves</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/f